# Finnhub API Configuration
# Get your free API key at https://finnhub.io/
FINNHUB_API_KEY=d945dv9r01qj2ciaf4hgd945dv9r01qj2ciaf4i0
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Sign up for a free Finnhub account at https://finnhub.io/register
# 3. Get your API key from https://finnhub.io/dashboard
# 4. Replace 'your_finnhub_api_key_here' with your actual API key
# 5. The free tier allows ~60 calls/minute, sufficient for 40+ tickers
#
# Note: The agent REQUIRES a valid Finnhub API key to fetch news and sentiment.
# If the API fails or the key is invalid, the app will raise an error.

# Groq LLM API Configuration
# Get your free API key at https://console.groq.com/
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
# Instructions:
# 1. Sign up for a free Groq account at https://console.groq.com/
# 2. Get your API key from the Groq dashboard
# 3. Replace 'your_groq_api_key_here' with your actual API key
# 4. The free tier provides fast inference for LLM-based sentiment analysis
#
# Note: The agent uses Groq to generate AI-powered rationales and news analysis.
# If the API fails or the key is invalid, the app will raise an error.
